(18892, 'Feburic 40 mg 20 f.c. tablets', 'فيبيوريك 40مجم 20 قرص', '29', '76', 'Febuxostat', 'Hikma pharma', 'Tablet', 'أقراص', 'علاج النقرص -- علاج الالام والالتهابات الناتجة عن النقرص بالمفاصل و الكعبين', 'Antigout', '40 mg', 'Febuxostat is indicated for the chronic management of hyperuricemia in adult patients with gout who have an inadequate response to a maximally titrated dose of [allopurinol], who are intolerant to allopurinol, or for whom treatment with allopurinol is not advisable.[L46073] It is not recommended for the treatment of asymptomatic hyperuricemia [L32238] or secondary hyperuricemia.[A230583]', '6221000000577', '', 8814, '2024-11-16', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
